message.body: Hey! Just back and am at Beau tonight. Arnie dropped off ######## If you're in the hood, come get it. Otherwise, I'm working a double at Beau on Sat, and Sun brunch. Working bar Sat night. If you come then, I'll buy you a nice stiff drink:-)
I will have to come by this weekend cuz I'm sick :(
Glad you made it back in one piece
Sorry to hear you're not feeling well:-( Come find me this weekend if you're up to it. Either way, I have your moolah. And some tokens too:-)))
Yes! Thank you, see u soon
I forgot to ask if you have the spare key for Zoe?
Great. Can you bring that when we do the money exchange?
